10. AR and Immersive Shopping Experiences
Augmented Reality (AR) and immersive technologies are redefining online shopping in 2026. AR allows customers to visualize products in real-world environments before making a purchase.
Examples include:
•	Virtual try-ons for fashion and accessories
•	3D product previews
•	Interactive product demonstrations
Immersive experiences reduce purchase hesitation, increase confidence, and lower return rates.
